bio:
Founder and CEO of Universo da Cor (www.universodacor.com.br) - a color research center based in Sao Paulo (Brazil) that advises companies and offers extension courses on color application and color composition. Attended by professionals, educators and students, Universo da Cor will soon launch on-line courses.
Lilian is the author of innovative methodologies for extension courses on color application in several design specialties, such as: "Color Indoors" and "Color on the Facades" for architects and interior designers, "Color in Self Image" for image consulting professionals and "Color in Surface Design" to fashion and textile designers; and has developed and designed special didactic material for the teaching of color perception and composition, as the Kit Projetando com a Cor (Designing with Color Kit), a set of specific color plates for composition experiments that turned out to be also a professional tool acquired by architects and designers to improve their color composition skills;
Her courses at Universo da Cor are nationally recognized and requested by several educational institutions, professional associations and companies, as shown in the next topics.
